    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Copy",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "Port Allegany, Pa.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "November 18, 1947.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "Federal Bureau of Investigation,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "Pittsburgh, Pa.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Gentlemen:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Following the appearance in this town on November 6, 1947,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "of a Mr. [REDACTED], Red Cross,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Pittsburgh, Pa. as \"speaker of the evening\", at the annual local",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Red Cross dinner, I was told by Dr. [REDACTED], local practicing",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "dentist, that in a personal conversation, following the dinner, Mr.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "[REDACTED] told him that the \"saucers\" reported as seen in various",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "parts of the country, were actually from Spain. He said that Mr.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "[REDACTED] said that this had been ascertained by the Government in",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Washington, but that it was not being made known. He said that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] had been in Europe and inferred that he had been in",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Spain and knew conditions over there. Dr. [REDACTED] is a man active",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "in the Methodist Chruch and the local Protestant Mens Club, and it is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "easy to see how far this report can be spread. The fact that the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "Federal Government indorses the Red Cross makes a statement of an official",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "representative of that organization almost indisputable.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "As a representative of the Federal Government and as a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "citizen interested in truth and World peace and racial and religious",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "harmony in our own country, I question the advisability of an accredited",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "representative of the Red Cross giving out this information, even \"off",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "the record\". I thought you might be able to check with Mr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "or his organization.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "Yours very truly,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "[REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
